    V3.1.23: RAPID REGIME DETECTION
    
    Changes:
    1. Lock reduced from 30 min to 10 min
    2. MOMENTUM OVERRIDE: If BTC 4h change > 1.5%, IMMEDIATE switch (bypass hysteresis)
